    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sweet potato is cooking, dice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely, then separate the whites from the<strong> </strong>greens</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
